    Game Notes:
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
    This amazing simulation will leave you in disbelief with its innovative
    new 3D engine. It looks and feels just like you are playing real darts!
    Challenge and defeat a variety of unique opponents on your quest to
    capture the ultimate prize: The Tournament Champions trophy! 
    
    Game Features:
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    - Custom 3D graphics engine
    - Customized characters, each with different skill levels 
    - Up to 10 different match games with scoring between 101 and 1001. Also
      includes fun games like Cricket and Around the Clock
    - Different levels allow you to play at home, in a pub, or compete in a
      tournament 
    - In-game statistics tracking allows you to follow your own progress 
    - Easy-to-use interface and in-game hints make learning the game quick
      and easy for beginners 
    - Adjustable music, sound effects and menus enable you to customize the
      games appearance
